Perl MorphoDiTa Bindings
========================

%!encoding: utf-8

To compile Perl bindings, run ``make`` in the ``bindings/perl`` directory,
optionally with the described Make options. Perl 5.8 and later is supported.

Path to the include headers of the required Perl version must be specified
in the ``PERL_INCLUDE`` variable using
``` make PERL_INCLUDE=path_to_Perl_includes
